trans-unit.source: dictionary. Supported options are shown below.

refers to the location of a version.json file in the host S3 bucket. The versions displayed in the version selector are generated from this JSON file via an AJAX call. You only need to update one file to make the change across all versions. Generating the JSON is left up to the implementor (i.e., you), but it can be incorporated into a CI/CD process. Ideally, the JSON should be at the root of the project directory in S3, with versions being in subfolders as shown here:
